// Markdown lint config for the BugStalker fork's docs.
//
// `BUGSTALKER.md` deliberately uses long lines for the cargo/launch
// JSON snippets (which would lose readability if hard-wrapped at
// 80 cols) and a wide settings table. We disable the line-length
// rule and let prose wrap to author taste.
{
    "config": {
        "MD013": false
    },
    "globs": [
        "BUGSTALKER.md"
    ]
}
